WEBVTT

00:01:29.506 --> 00:01:33.212
And I developed films,
and I made enlargements.

00:01:34.633 --> 00:01:39.045
One day, when I was 15 years old,

00:01:39.069 --> 00:01:41.954
I was arrested by the gestapo

00:01:41.978 --> 00:01:44.601
and beaten up,

00:01:44.625 --> 00:01:47.826
and, for two months,
dragged through various prisons,

00:01:47.850 --> 00:01:51.603
and eventually, I ended up

00:01:51.627 --> 00:01:57.942
in a 150-year-old fortress
in Czechoslovakia,

00:01:57.966 --> 00:02:02.339
which the Nazis had converted
into a concentration camp.